pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$bgLight"
elements:
  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 40, 900, 50]
    content:
      style: "$pageTitle"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>3 قطاعات أولوية تشتري بسرعة</strong></p>

  - elementId: title-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 95, 80, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: sector-1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 120, 370, 380]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardBg"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$cardBorder"

  - elementId: sector-1-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [85, 145, 40, 40]
    iconName: "fas:bullhorn"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: sector-1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [85, 200, 320, 35]
    content:
      fontSize: 22
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>وكالات التسويق</strong></p>

  - elementId: sector-1-pain
    elementType: text
    bounds: [85, 245, 320, 95]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$textMutedLight"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>• Leads تضيع بدون متابعة</p>
        <p>• يحتاجون Proof لعملائهم</p>
        <p>• Follow-up ضعيف أو معدوم</p>

  - elementId: sector-1-solution
    elementType: text
    bounds: [85, 350, 320, 50]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><span style="color:$primary;"><strong>الحل:</strong></span> نظام يثبت أين تضيع فرص عملائك + تقارير أسبوعية</p>

  - elementId: sector-2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [455, 120, 370, 380]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardBg"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$cardBorder"

  - elementId: sector-2-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [480, 145, 40, 40]
    iconName: "fas:graduation-cap"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: sector-2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 200, 320, 35]
    content:
      fontSize: 22
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>شركات التدريب</strong></p>

  - elementId: sector-2-pain
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 245, 320, 95]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$textMutedLight"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>• واتساب مليان استفسارات</p>
        <p>• تحويل ضعيف للتسجيلات</p>
        <p>• حملات موسمية بدون نظام</p>

  - elementId: sector-2-solution
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 350, 320, 50]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><span style="color:$primary;"><strong>الحل:</strong></span> نظام متابعة وتحويل استفسارات → تسجيلات مدفوعة</p>

  - elementId: sector-3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [850, 120, 370, 380]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardBg"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$cardBorder"

  - elementId: sector-3-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [875, 145, 40, 40]
    iconName: "fas:briefcase"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: sector-3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [875, 200, 320, 35]
    content:
      fontSize: 22
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>شركات B2B Services</strong></p>

  - elementId: sector-3-pain
    elementType: text
    bounds: [875, 245, 320, 95]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$textMutedLight"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>• صفقات بطيئة</p>
        <p>• CRM ضعيف أو غير مستخدم</p>
        <p>• مؤسس لا يرى الحقيقة</p>

  - elementId: sector-3-solution
    elementType: text
    bounds: [875, 350, 320, 50]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><span style="color:$primary;"><strong>الحل:</strong></span> War Room يوضح الفرص والتأخيرات لكل صفقة</p>

  - elementId: market-note
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 530, 1160, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$textMutedLight"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>🎯 السوق السعودي B2B في مرحلة تحول رقمي سريع — الشركات تبحث عن حلول عملية لا أدوات معقدة</p>

  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1180, 680, 60, 25]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$textMuted"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>05</p>

  - elementId: bottom-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 716, 1280, 4]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"
